            <div class="title">
                Profits Tax Bill
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1949-11-03/debates/8f32b017-dba0-49b3-84af-23a633469a96/DoubleTaxationRelief" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
