<p class="">Yes, I thought so. Quite a lot has happened since 1927.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d2137f6f-c29a-4033-bd59-5085e3b3a1e0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
