<p class="">I apologise for intervening again, but I would point out that those figures were calculated before the introduction of this Profits Tax.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-634ad8a5-6e57-405e-8d59-9f145f43c008" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
