<p class="">I hesitate to interrupt the hon. Member, he being such an excellent and controversial debater, but the proposal in this Bill is to reduce profits by taxation. There is no suggestion here to increase profits, but to reduce them.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
