<p class="">I wonder if the hon. Gentleman would be prepared to deny the arguments of his friends on his side of the House when they declared that this tax will damage trade?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-0d0bb5ee-b48c-4dca-9cd7-632aa8d41620" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
