                Mr. Assheton
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-26645a85-f155-4f89-8917-18d4986d30e5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-11-03/debates/560d9054-37e5-4c45-a128-3defb98dfe05/ProfitsTaxBill#contribution-26645a85-f155-4f89-8917-18d4986d30e5">
