<p class=""><em>rose</em>—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-62d7c262-a93f-442f-9bf6-2d2ea68870bd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
